---
// Hero.astro — full-width hero with 12-col asymmetric grid
// Image served from public/ via root-relative path (static build, no ESM import needed)
---

<section class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-gutter py-xl md:py-xxl">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-xl items-center">

    <!-- Portrait column: col-span-5 -->
    <div class="md:col-span-5 h-[500px] md:h-[700px] bg-warm-white relative border border-border-subtle">
      <img
        src="/assets/images/luis-jimenez.png"
        alt="Luis Jiménez Camacho"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        width="600"
        height="700"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Text column: col-span-7 -->
    <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col items-start">

      <!-- Eyebrow -->
      <div class="font-metadata text-metadata text-steel mb-md uppercase tracking-wider">
        INVESTIGACIÓN PRIVADA · OSINT · EVIDENCIA LEGAL
      </div>

      <!-- H1 -->
      <h1 class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg text-primary mb-lg">
        La verdad<br />no se adivina.<br />Se investiga.
      </h1>

      <!-- Body -->
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-xl max-w-reading-width">
        Desplegamos inteligencia táctica y análisis forense para corporaciones, firmas legales y clientes privados. Operamos bajo estricto protocolo de confidencialidad, transformando información difusa en evidencia accionable.
      </p>

      <!-- CTAs -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-md">
        <a
          class="bg-ink-blue text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps px-lg py-md rounded-none uppercase text-center hover:bg-ink-hover transition-colors duration-150"
          href="#intake"
        >
          Iniciar consulta
        </a>
        <a
          class="ghost-button font-label-caps text-label-caps px-lg py-md rounded-none uppercase text-center transition-colors duration-150"
          href="#servicios"
        >
          Áreas de práctica
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Mono detail strip -->
      <div class="mt-xl font-metadata text-metadata text-steel uppercase tracking-wider">
        LIC. CLASS C #C2700XXX · FLORIDA, USA · EST. 2014
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
